info.name: zap2it TV overschedule
info.description: Every once in awhile, zap2it adds a network to my lineup that isn't even part of my selected provider - I couldn't watch it if I wanted to. This zaps the pointless listings from my lineup.
info.additionalInfo: 2014.11.30 - I've been doing this offline for a while, but it's getting messy to maintain all the local styles.
